{"id":17930,"date":"2022-12-31T04:19:09","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:19:09","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:09","slug":"tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-2\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00ednh n\u0103ng hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1edf k\u00ednh xe t\u1eeb xa hay xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ngang nh\u01b0 v\u00e0o cua l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu xe.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u00d4 t\u00f4 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m s\u1ebd gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 trong phim khoa h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u1edfng.  Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1eefu \u00edch, gi\u1ea3m phi\u1ec1n ph\u1ee9c cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n nh\u1edd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf th\u00f4ng minh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn.  Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u1ec7n d\u1ee5ng n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00edt m\u1eabu xe tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">\u0110\u00f3ng\/m\u1edf c\u1eeda k\u00ednh t\u1eeb xa:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4\" title=\"tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4<\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">\u0110\u00f3ng m\u1edf c\u1eeda k\u00ednh Volkswagen th\u00f4ng qua ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a.  Video: Lurgs C\u00e1ch H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu xe c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Volkswagen v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00e3ng kh\u00e1c gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i xe ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 thi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i do l\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 khi kh\u00f3a xe.  \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1edd t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1edf k\u00ednh t\u1eeb xa th\u00f4ng qua ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u1eafng n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 xe ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eadu ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.  Ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef n\u00fat m\u1edf kh\u00f3a v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng, gi\u00fap h\u1ea1 nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 cabin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o xe.  Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e0i x\u1ebf c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o xe n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u1ebb c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 x\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Xe qua nh\u01b0 cua:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_239_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4\" title=\"1672442045_239_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_239_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_239_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_239_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4<\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Video: GMC<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean xe \u0111i\u1ec7n Hummer EV, ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0o cua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng 4 b\u00e1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap chi\u1ebfc b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y ch\u00e9o, khi c\u1ea3 b\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u00e1nh sau quay v\u1ec1 c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t h\u01b0\u1edbng.  ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Th\u00e1ng 12\/2019, m\u1ed9t h\u00e3ng xe \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Rivian c\u0169ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u00ean m\u1eabu b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i R1T.  Xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4 t\u00f4 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 xe t\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">R1T c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 R1S l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1edd c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u00e1nh xe.  Khi quay, 2 b\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng ph\u00eda s\u1ebd \u1edf ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng, 2 b\u00e1nh c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00f9i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Thay th\u1ebf ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_748_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4\" title=\"1672442045_748_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_748_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_748_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442045_748_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4<\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Video: BMW<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kho\u1ea3ng 4-5 n\u0103m, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00e3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 t\u00ean Digital Key.  Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh thay cho ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu xe, v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 xe sang, nh\u01b0 BMW.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">H\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau g\u1eadp th\u1eb3ng:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442046_681_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4\" title=\"1672442046_681_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442046_681_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442046_681_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672442046_681_tinh-nang-hiem-co-tren-o-to.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean \u00f4 t\u00f4<\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Video: Honda<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe b\u00e1n t\u1ea3i ph\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Ford F-150 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Honda Jazz\/Fit c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Civic \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau g\u1eadp th\u1eb3ng thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 g\u1eadp ph\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng.  Nh\u1edd thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh linh ho\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng gian \u1edf h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 xe \u0111\u1ea1p.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Ford F-150, khi h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau g\u1eadp th\u1eb3ng, h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ea3 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 180 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh gi\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eb1m cho nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i khi c\u1ea7n tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh d\u00e0i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">M\u1ef9 Anh (theo Carscoops)<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1edf k\u00ednh xe t\u1eeb xa hay xe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ngang nh\u01b0 v\u00e0o cua l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eabu xe. \u00d4 t\u00f4 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ra m\u1eaft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m s\u1ebd gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 trong phim khoa h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u1edfng. Tuy [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16167,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17930"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17930"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17930\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16167"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17930"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17930"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17930"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}